    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your wit can drive people into a rage directed solely at you. When you use this feat, you spend two actions berating and belittling a human target. Attempt an Intimidation skill check against the target's Will DC. If you succeed, the target becomes enraged and takes a -2 circumstance penalty when attacking anyone except you (-4 on a critical success). This penalty lasts until you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious}, or the target hits you with a critical hit.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.hopefinder.effects.HZMvFstS4np7q83t]{Effect: Insulted}</p>",
